title: Mississippi Mass Choir - We Have Seen His Star 320cbr
description:
Source: 2007 CD
-
Mississippi Mass Choir - We Have Seen His Star 320cbr (Big Papi) 2007 Southern Baptist Gospel Christmas Music

-
Jackson, MS church gospel choir that has released quite a few CD's. If you are into that old time black gospel music then this is your download :) Listening to this reminded me of how many singers like Whitney Houston got their start in the music business. - Big Papi
